193
00:15:13.317 --> 00:15:14.511
Destiny.

194
00:15:14.852 --> 00:15:16.046
Destiny?

195
00:15:17.354 --> 00:15:18.946
You've been asking me
about my motives.

196
00:15:19.056 --> 00:15:20.580
- Right. Right.
- My methods.

197
00:15:22.126 --> 00:15:23.684
They're all connected.

198
00:15:24.361 --> 00:15:25.794
Everything's connected.

199
00:15:25.896 --> 00:15:28.194
Okay.
How was Claire Kuchever connected?

200
00:15:28.298 --> 00:15:29.765
I needed a car.

201
00:15:29.867 --> 00:15:31.425
