- No. well. something

202
00:15:31.535 --> 00:15:33.503
- that couldn't be traced back to me.
- Right.

203
00:15:33.604 --> 00:15:36.368
I had one ready till that cop showed up.

204
00:15:37.007 --> 00:15:39.635
That cop was a federal agent.

205
00:15:39.743 --> 00:15:42.109
Lawrence Minuti. My partner.
You shot him.

206
00:15:42.212 --> 00:15:45.181
He... I was about to burn him
and he was waking up. you know?

207
00:15:45.282 --> 00:15:46.874
I mean. I'm not cruel.

208
00:15:49.386 --> 00:15:53.524
Well. why didn't you "do that"
for Claire Kuchever?

209
00:15:55.225 --> 00:16:00.686
Well. because I needed her
to look like a ferry victim.

210
00:16:00.798 --> 00:16:03.159
- and a bullet would've given it away.
- I see.

211
00:16:03.267 --> 00:16:06.600
I went to her house
on the pretense of buying her car.

212
00:16:06.703 --> 00:16:09.934
I took her from behind. taped her mouth
and threw a hood over her head.

213
00:16:10.040 --> 00:16:11.007
Then?

214
00:16:11.108 --> 00:16:14.134
I bound her wrists and her ankles
and I drove her back to my place.

215
00:16:14.244 --> 00:16:16.075
I loaded the device into her car

216
00:16:16.180 --> 00:16:17.738
and then I soaked her
with the gasoline.

217
00:16:17.848 --> 00:16:18.940
Jesus.

218
00:16:19.049 --> 00:16:20.073
And?

219
00:16:20.317 --> 00:16:21.716
I think you know
what happened after that.

220
00:16:21.819 --> 00:16:23.719
No. I don't know. I want you to tell me.
You gotta talk.

221
00:16:23.821 --> 00:16:25.846
I mean. you know. come on. hero.
What happened after that?

222
00:16:25.956 --> 00:16:27.116
I'll tell you what happened after that.

223
00:16:27.224 --> 00:16:30.660
You killed 543 people.
How do you feel about that?

224
00:16:35.799 --> 00:16:39.428
I think that you were a murderer
right from the beginning.

225
00:16:41.939 --> 00:16:45.500
Sometimes a little human collateral
is the cost of freedom.

226
00:16:45.609 --> 00:16:47.474
To me.
those people were war casualties.

227
00:16:47.578 --> 00:16:49.478
but to you. they're just evidence.

228
00:16:49.580 --> 00:16:52.014
That'll do. We got him.

229
00:16:52.115 --> 00:16:53.082
What'd you say?

230
00:16:53.317 --> 00:16:57.048
You think you know what's coming?
You don't have a clue.

231
00:16:57.154 --> 00:16:59.145
