00:39:02.376 --> 00:39:06.642
- I think that's gonna stay. Is that okay?
- Yeah. it's great.

492
00:39:06.747 --> 00:39:07.714
Okay.

493
00:39:09.750 --> 00:39:13.413
- All right. I'm not very good at this.
- You're very good.

494
00:39:27.034 --> 00:39:28.729
What's the matter?

495
00:39:29.770 --> 00:39:31.067
Jesus.

496
00:39:34.641 --> 00:39:36.632
I haven't changed a thing.

497
00:39:37.811 --> 00:39:40.041
I gotta go. And you gotta go with me.
Come on.

498
00:39:40.147 --> 00:39:41.375
What?

499
00:39:41.882 --> 00:39:44.350
- I thought you said I was safe now.
- I was wrong. I was wrong.

500
00:39:44.451 --> 00:39:46.214
You gotta go with me now. Right now.

501
00:39:47.421 --> 00:39:49.582
Wait. wait. wait! Don't answer it.

502
00:39:51.792 --> 00:39:53.191
Don't answer it. I'll prove it to you.

503
00:39:53.293 --> 00:39:54.351
That's your friend Beth calling.

504
00:39:54.461 --> 00:39:55.951
Let the machine pick it up.
She's gonna say.

505
00:39:56.063 --> 00:39:59.624
"Hi. Claire. It's Beth. Are you there?
I'm sorry to call you so early.

506
00:39:59.733 --> 00:40:02.759
"but when you didn't call me last night
I got worried."

507
00:40:03.303 --> 00:40:06.033
Claire? Hi. it's Beth. Are you there?

508
00:40:06.139 --> 00:40:07.538
I'm sorry to call you so early.

509
00:40:07.641 --> 00:40:09.666
but you said you were gonna call me
when you got home.

510
00:40:09.776 --> 00:40:11.539
and when you didn't.
I started to get worried.

511
00:40:11.645 --> 00:40:13.306
- Beth. is this a joke?
- Oh. hey. hey! No.

512
00:40:13.413 --> 00:40:15.210
Like I said. I was just worried
about you. that's all.

513
00:40:15.315 --> 00:40:17.340
I can't talk right now.
Someone's here. I'll call you later.

514
00:40:17.451 --> 00:40:18.418
Claire...

515
00:40:18.518 --> 00:40:21.681
Believe me. the only one
you're gonna be safe with is me.

516
00:40:21.855 --> 00:40:23.482
- Okay.
- Let's go.

517
00:40:28.695 --> 00:40:29.787
I don't understand.

518
00:40:29.896 --> 00:40:33.491
Why not just call the police
and have them arrest him at the dock?

519
00:40:34.067 --> 00:40:36.365
He'll set the bomb off
right there on the spot.

520
00:40:36.470 --> 00:40:37.994
He can't know he's been compromised

521
00:40:38.105 --> 00:40:40.096
until it's too late for him
to do anything about it.

522
00:40:40.207 --> 00:40:42.937
He'll set the timer. walk away on foot.
get on his motorcycle

523
00:40:43.043 --> 00:40:45.910
and ride to the Crescent City Bridge
to watch.

524
00:40:46.012 --> 00:40:49.675
Okay. then what?
You defuse the bomb?

525
00:40:50.183 --> 00:40:52.048
Then I defuse the bomb.

526
00:41:50.510 --> 00:41:52.341
There's my truck.

527
00:42:01.988 --> 00:42:03.853
- All these people.
- There he is.

528
00:42:03.957 --> 00:42:05.288
Where?

529
00:42:05.425 --> 00:42:08.451
You see the military jacket
coming this way?

530
00:42:12.499 --> 00:42:14.296
It's just what you said.

531
00:42:14.401 --> 00:42:17.632
All right.
you see those officers behind you?

532
00:42:17.737 --> 00:42:19.830
- Yeah.
- When the ferry pulls off.

533
00:42:19.940 --> 00:42:22.431
I want you to tell them about the bomb.
all right?

534
00:42:22.542 --> 00:42:24.908
- They'll believe me?
- They better believe you.

535
00:42:25.011 --> 00:42:27.241
- Come on. they'll arrest me.
- They won't arrest you.

536
00:42:27.347 --> 00:42:30.976
They'll take you into custody.
You'll be fine. That's a good thing.

537
00:42:31.384 --> 00:42:32.749
Don't turn around.

538
00:42:39.359 --> 00:42:40.553
Doug...

539
00:42:43.630 --> 00:42:44.995
Be careful.

540
00:43:17.964 --> 00:43:19.795
Your attention. please.

541
00:43:19.899 --> 00:43:22.424
Passengers are not allowed
on the car deck

542
00:43:22.535 --> 00:43:25.163
when the ferry is in motion.

543
00:43:31.845 --> 00:43:33.335
Sir! Sir.

544
00:43:33.446 --> 00:43:36.006
Excuse me. sir. you're gonna
have to move to the upper deck.

545
00:43:36.116 --> 00:43:38.710
- Passengers aren't allowed here.
- Okay.

546
00:44:18.158 --> 00:44:20.319
Can't believe it. They're right on time.

547
00:44:20.427 --> 00:44:22.759
Let's get these boys to their party.

548
00:44:45.452 --> 00:44:47.283
Mama!

549
00:46:29.873 --> 00:46:32.000
Excuse me. sir? Sir!

550
00:46:32.109 --> 00:46:35.476
There's no passengers allowed
on the car deck during transit.

551
00:46:38.782 --> 00:46:41.012
No passengers allowed. sir.

552
00:46:55.399 --> 00:46:56.559
Let's go! Let's go!

553
00:47:54.324 --> 00:47:56.019
It's destiny. Oerstadt.

554
00:47:56.893 --> 00:48:00.056
Satan reasons like a man.
but God thinks of eternity.

555
00:48:02.799 --> 00:48:04.266
What did you say?

556
00:48:04.368 --> 00:48:08.031
I'm saying it's gonna take
a little divine intervention here. buddy.

557
00:48:10.040 --> 00:48:11.632
I'm coming out.

558
00:48:19.783 --> 00:48:21.375
What'd you say?

559
00:48:22.519 --> 00:48:24.419
I thought you were a patriot.

560
00:48:24.521 --> 00:48:25.749
Oh. I am.

561
00:48:26.957 --> 00:48:29.152
Patriotism requires sacrifice.

562
00:48:29.760 --> 00:48:33.025
- I'm willing to sacrifice.
- Yeah? Who? Her? Me?

563
00:48:33.130 --> 00:48:35.690
You're willing to sacrifice others.
but not yourself.

564
00:48:35.799 --> 00:48:40.168
The Tree of Liberty must be refreshed
with the blood of patriots and tyrants.

565
00:48:41.471 --> 00:48:42.438
Right.

566
00:48:42.539 --> 00:48:46.270
Sometimes a little human collateral
is the cost of freedom. isn't it?

567
00:48:51.315 --> 00:48:53.283
Who are you. Oerstadt?

568
00:48:56.253 --> 00:48:57.618
Who are you?

569
00:49:00.390 --> 00:49:02.449
It's not supposed to be this way.

570
00:49:30.354 --> 00:49:31.981
You all right?

571
00:49:35.158 --> 00:49:38.059
- I killed him.
- No. you didn't. I did.

572
00:49:38.161 --> 00:49:41.028
It's 10:48
on Fat Tuesday. Mardi Gras.

573
00:49:41.131 --> 00:49:43.725
Now let's go back in time to 1964.

574
00:49:43.834 --> 00:49:45.927
- We're gonna die.
- No. we're not.

575
00:49:46.036 --> 00:49:48.504
...on 105.3 FM.
the heart of New Orleans.

576
00:49:48.605 --> 00:49:50.470
Hit the gas.

577
00:49:50.640 --> 00:49:52.073
Hit the gas!

578
00:49:57.781 --> 00:50:01.376
Put your hands in the air
and step out of the vehicle now!

579
00:50:03.086 --> 00:50:05.486
We get out now. everybody dies.

580
00:50:06.990 --> 00:50:09.185
You have until the count of three!

581
00:50:09.292 --> 00:50:10.316
Hit it.

582
00:50:10.427 --> 00:50:11.485
One...

583
00:52:24.127 --> 00:52:27.585
But my daughter's on that ferry.
Please. Please.

584
00:52:28.765 --> 00:52:30.960
Oh. God. my daughter!

585
00:52:45.482 --> 00:52:46.915
Chrissie!

586
00:52:47.784 --> 00:52:48.773
Chrissie!

587
00:52:48.885 --> 00:52:51.285
- Oh. Chrissie! Chrissie!
- It's my mom!

588
00:52:51.388 --> 00:52:52.480
Mom!

589
00:52:58.562 --> 00:53:01.793
Ma'am? We're gonna need you
to stay right here.

590
00:53:01.898 --> 00:53:03.991
Someone's on the way over
to take a statement

591
00:53:04.100 --> 00:53:06.466
and ask you some questions. okay?

592
00:53:31.394 --> 00:53:33.624
- Bobby.
- Doug.

593
00:53:33.730 --> 00:53:35.129
- How you doing?
- All right.

594
00:53:35.231 --> 00:53:37.722
Got a live one over here.
Pulled her out of the drink.

595
00:53:37.834 --> 00:53:40.200
Somehow involved in all of this.

596
00:53:44.007 --> 00:53:45.099
Okay.

597
00:53:50.914 --> 00:53:53.678
- How you doing?
- Doug?

598
00:53:54.784 --> 00:53:56.217
That's right.

599
00:53:59.556 --> 00:54:01.547
- You okay?
- Yeah.

600
00:54:06.363 --> 00:54:07.728
Have we met?

601
00:54:09.633 --> 00:54:12.397
Yeah. Yeah. we have.

602
00:54:16.272 --> 00:54:17.899
It's okay. Come on.

603
00:54:18.842 --> 00:54:20.036
Come on.

604
00:54:35.158 --> 00:54:36.955
- You okay?
- Yeah.

605
00:54:37.060 --> 00:54:38.721
- You sure?
- Yeah.

606
00:54:39.029 --> 00:54:41.691
Okay. I'll get you warmed up.

607
00:54:51.641 --> 00:54:52.972
What is it?

608
00:54:54.744 --> 00:54:56.075
What is it?

609
00:55:01.317 --> 00:55:02.375
Doug.

610
00:55:04.521 --> 00:55:08.184
What if you had to tell someone
the most important thing in the world.

611
00:55:08.291 --> 00:55:10.987
but you knew they'd never believe you?

612
00:55:12.362 --> 00:55:13.556
I'd try.

613
00:55:23.339 --> 00:55:24.431
No.
